      ],
      "relationships": "One-to-many (e.g., Company to JobPostings), Many-to-many (e.g., Students to Skills via StudentSkills, Jobs to Skills via JobSkills), One-to-one (e.g., User to Student/Recruiter/PlacementOfficer)."
